notesStmt.note: This conversation between two exchange students takes place at a pub. The two students have just met and talk about a miscellany of topics such as tourism in S1's hometown, settling into a new city, and reasons for coming to study in Vienna.

equipment.p: Portable minidisc recorder with electret condenser stereo microphone
